{"tid":2266070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"投給拜登就是摧毀賓州！ 川普造勢猛攻能源議題","createTime":"2020-11-01T04:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T08:42:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c1074e2346d1827d5e0e29967b73212aabd45c64","tid":2266070,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"根據《福斯新聞》 報導，川普於於美國時間10月31日前往賓州舉辦造勢活動，包括巴克斯郡（Bucks）、瑞丁（Reading）、巴特勒郡（Butler）、蒙圖斯維爾（Montoursville）等地。川普在巴特勒郡的造勢集會中指出，稍早他已經簽署一項行政命令，藉此保護賓州使用「水力壓裂法」開採頁岩油，並阻止任何人破壞賓州能源生產的努力。<br />\n<br />\n由於賓州允許選民在選舉日當天簽名撤回郵寄選票，並且親自投票，川普也在巴克斯郡向選民喊話，強調賓州選民有機會在週二（3日）改選他來「拯救美國夢」，川普直言：「美國獨立故事從這州開始，想一想，賓州是美國憲法簽署的州，從現在開始的3天，此舉將挽救美國夢」，川普也警告，有許多「腐敗勢力」試圖利用拜登來取代他。<br />\n<br />\n川普除了造勢集會外，也在推特持續重砲轟擊拜登，川普表示，他簽署了保護「水力壓裂法」及石化工業的行政命令，這意味著工作和美國能源的獨立性，「『瞌睡喬』將禁止水力壓裂並摧毀美國的能源工作，他沒頭腦啊！」川普強調，投給拜登和賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）一票，就是禁止水力壓裂和採礦，完全摧毀賓州的一票。<br />\n<br />\n而川普也向賓州選民溫情喊話：「在過去的4年中，你已經看到我為你們而戰，而現在，我依靠你為我們的國家取得又一次歷史性勝利。投給我和共和黨就是投給美國夢！出門投票吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3338336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3338336&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=2b78d4a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3338336&h=89ed7c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3338336</a>"},{"pid":"8e28e4e12c0ea37de8d74412228ac0458cfb6e73","tid":2266070,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/trump-pennsylvania-american-dream\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-pennsylvania-american-dream&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=14e1280d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-pennsylvania-american-dream&h=d7d93b4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/trump-pennsylvania-american-dream</a>"},{"pid":"7f763d41c7eabb6af03af3655da58f817bb274f9","tid":2266070,"uid":26770,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"賓周成為捍衛人類文明的關鍵"},{"pid":"395a13934eb5e6e3a8e0d46f59c7807514c1c2a1","tid":2266070,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"有我豐臣西軍支持，拜登點會輸呢？<br />\n川普，川，德川也，老賊必敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55966ad24945f7887a427414824d7e053ab05021","tid":2266070,"uid":165339,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:21:26.000Z","msg":"捍衛賓州"},{"pid":"c863ba09e7409ba02e9941cacec0671596696802","tid":2266070,"uid":267494,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"如果賓州咁都輸<br />\n班人真係自斷賓州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04be1dd545228d9c62cd62884e1ee65db1ccce8c","tid":2266070,"uid":197563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHv1Xi2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHv1Xi2.png&h=78ab0acf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb1fa0a8ff3d3fc78529dae73509e9b83831fb8f","tid":2266070,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04be1dd545228d9c62cd62884e1ee65db1ccce8c","tid":2266070,"uid":197563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHv1Xi2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHv1Xi2.png&h=78ab0acf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=